SLS 26RS-1532 ORIGINAL
SB NO. 463
Proposed law establishes a procedure for the remote acknowledgment of documents that
have already been signed and are not required by law to be executed as authentic acts and
are not acts, transactions, or instruments that are excluded in present law.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 35:623(D); adds R.S. 35:623(E))
